    "headline": "Revvity (NYSE:RVTY) Surprises With Q1 CY2026 Sales",
    "summary": "Life sciences company Revvity (NYSE:RVTY) reported Q1 CY2026 results topping the market’s revenue expectations, with sales up 7% year on year to $711.1 million. On the other hand, the company’s full-year revenue guidance of $2.83 billion at the midpoint came in 5.2% below analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.04 per share was 2.5% above analysts’ consensus estimates.",
